Coleby Lombardo https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Coleby_Lombardo 0 Coleby Jason Lombardo (also credited as Coleby Lomardo, born September 7, 1978), is former child actor who appeared in nearly twenty productions. In 1988 he was nominated for Young Artist Award as Best Young Actor - Guest Starring in a Television Drama The Colbys.
